race.comment: MEET GEORGE (2) has been improving with racing this campaign and will be cherry-ripe now third run back from the spell. Is one from one over this seven-furlong trip and shapes as a leading contender. CARBONARA (8) just ran into one better at the Sunny Coast last time out and Jones sticks in the saddle following that last-start placing. Right in this contest. BRAVE MONARCH (1) broke the maiden status at the latest effort and will have taken some confidence from that victory. Can go right on with the job now. WORTHY ENUFF (5) has placed over this course and distance and gets some weight off with the 2kg claim. In the mix. MISHANI MOET (7) may provide some value for the exotics players.
